<p>&amp; to show his contempt of the German &amp; Turkish gunner's  he deliberately looped the loop, that must have made them mad for they fired for all they were worth at him but that was their share, they have brought aviation to a fine art now alright a chap seems safer in the air than on the land or water, all the while I was on the penisular  I never saw only one aeroplane hit  and that was a taube which one of our guns brought down towards the last of our stay at Anzac.<br/>Another idea I think that has been exploded &amp; that is that heavy gunfire brings rain. I think we had some bombardments there</p>
